<h1>Cobbers – Chewy Caramel</h1>

<p>Fancy some caramel wrapped in milk chocolate? Need to remove a filling from your teeth and can't afford a dentist? Cobbers are good for both! These all-time Aussie favourites are still available and taste just as good…they also still have the ability to remove fillings from teeth – something many of my customers today will mention before stocking up on these tasty treats.</p>

